-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Avalonia (https://github.com/AvaloniaUI/Avalonia)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Exclr8.Terminal is a control built on the Avalonia UI framework. The
rendering, input, layout, clipboard, and font-shaping infrastructure that
makes this control possible is Avalonia's. Avalonia is consumed as a NuGet
dependency; its license follows.

