-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
xterm.js (https://github.com/xtermjs/xterm.js)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The escape-sequence parser in Exclr8.Terminal is shaped by xterm.js's
EscapeSequenceParser and Paul Williams' xterm state diagram. The
implementation here is independent .NET code, but the structural debt to
xterm.js's design is real and worth naming. Their license follows.

